arChildNodes.szComment:
EXT. CALDEUM, MIDDAY
The PLAYER, LORATH, NEYRELLE, and DONAN approach INARIUS and his KNIGHTS.
Inarius turns to face the group, clearly displeased.

Inarius turns away again and gestures to dismiss the Knights. They begin to file out. 
Meanwhile, the group is stunned into silence. Neyrelle looks between her mentors in frustration and dismay. 
Are we really going to take that?

Donan hesitates. He is more sensitive to the consequences of provoking Inarius than Lorath is. He looks to Lorath. Are you sure?
Lorath nods darkly. Carefully, Donan retrieves the soulstone and holds it aloft. It shines in the light. Lorath points to it as he speaks.
They definitely have Inarius’ attention now. All of a sudden, he takes the stone, shocking the group.
He launches into the air and flies off in the direction of the palace. He leaves behind a sudden and eerie silence. The group struggles to process what just happened.
